Package: sen8r
Title: Convenient R interface for interacting with the SENAITE LIMS API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul", "Cleary", , "paul.cleary@ukhsa.gov.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: sen8r provides a clean, pipe-friendly and well-documented R interface for working with the SENAITE Laboratory Information Management System (LIMS) REST API. It simplifies authentication, querying, and data extraction so you can focus on analysis instead of HTTP requests.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
